text: Not a fan of the canteen below the school. Rather walk to north or south spine for better options as SBS is located in the middle. Take campus green for the fastest and cheapest way here. School wise, smell like hospital.
The fried rice in the omelette was a bit dry. Most likely due to the crowd so the cook might be in a rush to prepare the food.
The red bean paste buns in the canteen there are great
